                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18281023-104-off611 t18281023-104-crimeloc614"></join>. I lost a coat and a cloak from the passage of my house; about eight o'clock in the evening of the 25th of September, I was sitting in my drawing-room, and the servant brought me up this note - I sent my boy out, who brought back the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18281023-104-person613">
                  MARGARET 
                  HAYES
               <interp inst="t18281023-104-person613" type="surname" value="HAYES"></interp>
