                     <interp inst="t18281023-104-person613" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am servant to the prosecutor. The prisoner brought this note to me that evening; there was no direction on it - I asked who it was for - he said for my master; I took it up stairs, and when I returned, the prisoner was gone, and I missed these articles from the passage.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. Q. Do you know me again? A. Yes, I do.</p>
               <p>
            
